trans-unit.source: An abstract implementation of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint>.
Derive from this class to expose contracts that support workflow creation and bookmark resumption.
trans-unit.target: Utledet fra denne klassen for å vise kontrakter som støtter arbeidsflyten oppretting og bokmerke resumption.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowHostingEndpoint"></xref> class with the specified contract type.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowHostingEndpoint"> </xref> klassen med den angitte kontrakt-typen.

trans-unit.source: The type of the contract that defines the basic message exchange patterns for a workflow hosting operation.
trans-unit.target: Hva slags kontrakten som definerer grunnleggende meldingen exchange mønstre for en arbeidsflyt som er vert for operasjonen.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowHostingEndpoint"></xref> class with the specified contract type, binding, and endpoint address.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowHostingEndpoint"> </xref> klassen med den angitte kontrakt type, binding og endpoint adressen.

trans-unit.source: The service contract for the endpoint.
The binding for the endpoint.
The address of the endpoint.
Gets a collection of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.CorrelationQuery"></xref> instances .
Populate this collection with queries that are run when a message arrives on the endpoint to determine which workflow instance the message should be sent to.
trans-unit.target: Fyll ut denne samlingen med spørringer som kjøres når en melding på sluttpunktet å finne ut hvilke arbeidsflytforekomsten meldingen som skal sendes til.

trans-unit.source: This property does not need to be used if custom instance resolution is provided by overriding <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowHostingEndpoint.OnGetInstanceId%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Trenger ikke denne egenskapen brukes hvis egendefinert forekomst løsning ved å overstyre <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowHostingEndpoint.OnGetInstanceId%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowHostingEndpoint.OnGetInstanceId%2A>

trans-unit.source: A collection of correlation queries.
Override to create a new<xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowCreationContext"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Override til å opprette en ny<xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowCreationContext"> </xref> forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: The inputs to the service operation.
Provides the execution context of the service operation invoked.
The instance ID of the workflow instance being created.
The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowHostingEndpointResponseContext> object that can be used to send replies back to the message source for a request/reply contract.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowHostingEndpointResponseContext>objekt som kan brukes til å sende svar tilbake til meldingskilden for en forespørsel/svar-kontrakt.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowHostingEndpointResponseContext>

trans-unit.source: A workflow creation context object.
Override to return the instance ID for the workflow instance being created.
trans-unit.target: Overstyre Hvis du vil returnere forekomst-ID for arbeidsflytforekomsten som opprettes.

trans-unit.source: Return null to indicate that an instance ID should be automatically generated.
trans-unit.target: Returner null til å angi at en forekomst-ID skal genereres automatisk.

trans-unit.source: The inputs to the service operation.
The operation context of the service operation.
trans-unit.target: Operasjonen konteksten for en operasjon for tjeneste.

trans-unit.source: The instance ID for the newly created workflow instance.
Override to return a bookmark to be resumed on the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Overstyre Hvis du vil returnere et bokmerke for å fortsette på arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: The inputs to the service operation.
The execution context of the service operation being invoked.
The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowHostingResponseContext"></xref> object that can be used to send replies back to the message source for a request/reply contract.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Activities.WorkflowHostingResponseContext"> </xref> objekt som kan brukes til å sende svar tilbake til meldingskilden for en forespørsel/svar-kontrakt.

trans-unit.source: A value to be passed back to the workflow instance when the bookmark is resumed
trans-unit.target: En verdi som skal sendes til arbeidsflytforekomsten når bokmerket blir gjenopptatt

trans-unit.source: A bookmark.
